==============================================================================
 Fase 33 — Derivación del factor de normalización A
==============================================================================

 Convenciones:
   V_internal = 1.0³ = 1
   BOX_MPC_H  = 100.0 Mpc/h
   h (adim.)  = 0.674
   k_int ↔ k_hmpc: k_hmpc = k_int · h / BOX_MPC_H

 Cadena de factores (del estimador y del generador):
   [generador] σ(k)² = P_cont(k_phys) / N³         (amplitud)
   [generador] δ̂_k = σ · (g_r + i·g_i) → ⟨|δ̂|²⟩ = 2σ² = 2·P_cont/N³
   [generador] IFFT · (1/N³) → δ(x) real
   [CIC+FFT]   δ̂_DFT ≈ δ̂_generador (si partículas reproducen campo)
   [estimador] P_m = ⟨|δ̂|²⟩ · (V_int/N³)² / W²(k)
   ⇒ P_m ≈ 2·V² · P_cont(k_phys) / N⁹

 Predicción mínima (sin factor 2):   A_pred = V² / N⁹
 Con Hermitian (factor 2):           A_pred = 2·V²/N⁹
 Con conversión a (Mpc/h)³:          A_pred = 2·V² · BOX_MPC_H³ / N⁹

   N     A_min = V²/N⁹     A_herm = 2V²/N⁹     A_mpc = 2V²·B³/N⁹              N⁹
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   8        7.4506e-09          1.4901e-08            1.4901e-02       1.342e+08
  16        1.4552e-11          2.9104e-11            2.9104e-05       6.872e+10
  32        2.8422e-14          5.6843e-14            5.6843e-08       3.518e+13
  64        5.5511e-17          1.1102e-16            1.1102e-10       1.801e+16

 Contexto de los tests (reference Phase 32/33):
   A_obs(N=16³, 4 seeds) ≈ 3.3e-12
   A_obs(N=32³, 6 seeds) ≈ 1.66e-15
   log₁₀(A_obs/A_min) a N=32 ≈ -1.23
   ratio A(16)/A(32) observado ≈ 2000 vs predicho (32/16)⁹ = 512

Tabla numérica guardada en: experiments/nbody/phase33_pk_normalization/output/derivation_table.json
